</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-DOCTORS-GENOME-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
 UNDATED: the patient.''  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   In some cases, the course indicated by genetic testing will be
clear. If DNA analysis reveals an increased risk for skin or lung
