</P>
<P>
   CHICKENSOUP-SPOOF _ A spoof on ``Chicken Soup for the Chicken
Soul.'' It was a beautiful summer day, one I'll never forget. The
sun was round and gold like a big bowl of creamed corn. The sky was
blue like Clean `n' Clear astringent face wash for sensitive skin.
Fluffy puffs of clouds that looked like Farmer Brown's white hair
where it sticks out the back of his baseball cap floated along like
they had nowhere to go. Come to think of it, they probably didn't.
(Grand Junction Daily Sentinel). 12. MOVED
